[Student "S"]
{WEST, with 22 points and balanced, opens 2\C, expecting to rebid 2NT.

But EAST responds a positive 2NT, showing a balanced hand with 8 or more points.

WEST bids what his hand is worth, 3NT and EAST passes.}

