[Student "S"]
{WEST has a balanced hand with 11 points, so she responds 2NT to EAST's 2\C opening bid.

EAST bids 3NT. This shows 22-24 points, a hand he was planning to rebid 2NT.

WEST knows the side has at least 33 points, but no more than 35 so she bids 6NT.}

